\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 3. R. gredensis} (Cutanda & Willk.) Müller Arg. in DC., {\i Prodr. }{\b 16}({\b 2}): 582 (1868). Like {\b 2} but stems 10-25 cm, with axillary fascicles of leaves; leaves 3-12 × 0·5-1(-1·5) mm, lanceolate or narrow-lanceolate. 2n = 28.{\i  Montane pastures and gravelly places. • W.C. Spain} ({\i Sierra de Gredos}). Hs.
\par

