\pard\f0\fs28 Sect. LEUCORESEDA DC. Leaves pinnatifid; lobes usually varying irregularly in length. Sepals 5 or 6; petals 5 or 6 (two upper, two lateral, one or two lower), white, more or less clawed. Filaments persistent. Carpels 4.
\par

